Method Detail

serialize

public com.conceptwave.scripting.Boolean serialize(String key,
                                                   com.conceptwave.scripting.Integer timeout)
Blocks listener thread until any other thread executing with the same serialization key has completed. If multiple threads are blocked on the same serialization key, there is no gaurantee to the order threads will be released in.

Parameters:
key - Serialization key to block on.
timeout - Time to wait (in milliseconds) before failing serialization. A value of less than 1 means no wait at all.
Returns:
true if thread was successfully serialized. false if timeout expired.
